The paper deals with optimization of physical layer multicasting in large-scale multi-antenna arrays with per-antenna power constraints. This involves techniques from information theory (cs.IT), networking (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), and system optimization (cs.MM, cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
